<div class="page">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="badge">AI</div>
    <div class="hgroup">
      <h1>Telephony Integration (Pilot)</h1>
      <p class="sub">Twilio → Quirk Proxy (Caddy) → OpenAI Realtime.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Call flow</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Twilio number → TwiML Bin or Webhook → WebSocket connect to <code>wss://voice.quirkcars.com/realtime/twilio</code>.</li>
    <li>Caddy forwards to OpenAI Realtime with bidirectional streams.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Twilio setup</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Buy a number → Voice Configuration: TwiML Bin <i>or</i> Webhook.</li>
    <li>Primary handler: TwiML Bin (pilot), fallback: Webhook or 404.</li>
    <li>Recording off; media format PCM μ-law or Opus (as supported).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Testing</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Call the number; verify “press any key” and streaming events.</li>
    <li>Tail Caddy logs; confirm TLS and media return path.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr>
